messages.message: Sure, but it’s a pretty significant amount of work to do. We don’t have any split of the Results API in between Instabase Enterprise and AIHub rn. We’d have to add gating and testing of the gating to even just hide this single field.

Got it, it's a low priority cleanup anyways. I think we can leave it here for now and just document `model_confidence` better.

Have mentioned these in the proposal for app run results API - (WIP) PRD - App Run Results API - Google Docs (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-1UrTAgIMCqBm63c5BM_hJbjQSP2Uu8kpNJKMEfp558/edit).
